strings.Value: "It's so dark in here... This place gives me creeps! "
"I feel uncomfortableâ€¦ I'm not sure we're safe here. "
"It's beautiful, isn't it? It is in places like this that the frailty of faltering life grows clear!"
"Pull yourself together! Monsters can smell your fear. If you whine and moan, they'll eat you first!"
"I too feel disquieted. But together we're strong enough to stand against any danger."
"Don't be a chicken. I'll be right here."
